lyrics:
[Verse 1]
In a pixel world, where legends roam
Block by block, I'll make my own home
With a pick in hand, I'll search and find
Diamonds shining bright, deep in the mine

[Chorus]
Crafting my dreams, in a world of blocks
Minecraft adventure, rocks and blocks
Building, surviving, in this open range
Minecraft, my refuge, where I can change
